NoUI DERP POC

Stream S5: Verification Strategy Implementation Artifacts

**Claude Code Consumption-Ready Specifications**

*Version 1.0 \| February 2026*

Deliverable 1: Go Test Stub Templates

Five Go test files have been produced as companion artifacts to this
document. They follow the framework\'s structure with oracle comments,
complete input construction, and assertions on every output field.

  ------------------------------------------------ ----------- -----------------------------------
  **File**                                         **Tests**   **Coverage**

  rules/tier_determination_test.go                 12 tests    RULE-TIER-1/2/3 (Category 1)

  rules/eligibility_test.go                        28 tests    RULE-VESTING through
                                                               RULE-EARLY-REDUCE-T3 (Category 3)

  rules/benefit_calculation_test.go                20 tests    RULE-AMS-\* through RULE-ROUNDING
                                                               (Category 4)

  rules/supplemental_payment_dro_process_test.go   32 tests    Categories 5-8

  acceptance/demo_cases_test.go                    4 tests     End-to-end Cases 1-4

  integration/boundary_tests.go                    16 tests    4 architectural boundaries

  dataquality/data_quality_detection_test.go       12 tests    DQ-001 through DQ-006
  ------------------------------------------------ ----------- -----------------------------------

Total: 124 test functions covering all 52 rules, 4 demo cases, 4
boundaries, and 6 data quality issue types.

Deliverable 2: Boundary Case Inventory

For each of the 52 business rules, four required test cases with
specific input values and expected outputs. Cases follow the framework
pattern: Happy Path, Boundary, Just Below, and Negative.

